      <h1 class='title'>Asylum Seekers</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 cc112-3WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_112ws' title='Col. 112WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c112WS' name='column_112ws' href='#column_112ws' rel='bookmark'>112WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05304'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_580'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-jeremy-corbyn' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_580' title='Link to this speech by Mr Jeremy Corbyn' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <span class='question_no'>14.</span>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-jeremy-corbyn" title="Mr Jeremy Corbyn">Jeremy Corbyn</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05304">To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, how many asylum seekers are held in detention under immigration law. [134171]</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_113ws' title='Col. 113WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c113WS' name='column_113ws' href='#column_113ws' rel='bookmark'>113WS</a>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05305'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_581'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-beverley-hughes' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_581' title='Link to this speech by Ms Beverley Hughes' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-beverley-hughes" title="Ms Beverley Hughes">Beverley Hughes</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05305">As at 28 June, the most recent date of which published figures are available, there were a total of 1,690 individuals detained solely under Immigration Act powers. Of these, 1,355 were asylum seekers.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05306'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_582'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gwyn-prosser' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_582' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gwyn Prosser' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <span class='question_no'>17.</span>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gwyn-prosser" title="Mr Gwyn Prosser">Mr. Prosser</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05306">To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department what change there was in the number of asylum applications between October 2002 and September 2003. [134174]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05307'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_583'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-beverley-hughes' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_583' title='Link to this speech by Ms Beverley Hughes' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-beverley-hughes" title="Ms Beverley Hughes">Beverley Hughes</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05307">In June 2003, the most recent month for which published figures are available, there were 3,610 asylum applications, 59 per cent. lower than the 8,770 in October 2002<sup>1</sup>. Figures for July-September have not yet been finalised but we are confident that we will meet our commitment to halve intake in September 2003 compared with last October.</p><p id="S6CV0412P0-05308"><sup>1</sup> All figures exclude dependants.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
